commit 0dcd7876029b58770f769cbb7b484e88e4a305e5 upstream.

f7c83bcbfaf5 ("net: xfrm: use __this_cpu_read per-cpu helper") added a
__this_cpu_read() call inside ipcomp_alloc_tfms().

